title: OpenAI continues on its ‘code red’ warpath with new image generation model
description: OpenAI rolls out GPT Image 1.5 for ChatGPT, promising 4x faster generation, better instruction-following, and precise edits. The launch  escalates its rivalry with Google Gemini.
